item.description: Abstract This is the second version(Beta01) of my Blog Website design. Bugs: contents won’t display at bottle of the homepage, such as “C 2021” things didn’t sync to Github, such as the posts are invisible at homepage, titles are still default on the “Posts” page when the web is released.
